== Not banned ==
Typical revisionist bullshit. Tamo daleko was never banned. Ethnic folk songs were explicitly *encouraged* in the SFRY. [[Special:Contributions/2620:15C:6:16:69A2:2EF5:5512:8381|2620:15C:6:16:69A2:2EF5:5512:8381]] ([[User talk:2620:15C:6:16:69A2:2EF5:5512:8381|talk]]) 19:07, 28 September 2015 (UTC)

== not serbian song ==

this is a traditional croatian folk song that was adopted and revised to suit serbian expansonist ideology!  here are the original lyrics:  
Tamo daleko, daleko kraj mora,
tamo je selo moje, tamo je ljubav moja.
Hajdemo, dušo, da sretno živimo mi,
jer mladost prolazi žurno i taj život nesretni.
Tamo daleko, gdje cvijeću nema kraj,
tamo je selo moje, tamo je vječiti raj.  <span style="font-size: smaller;" class="autosigned">— Preceding [[Wikipedia:Signatures|unsigned]] comment added by [[Special:Contributions/38.112.92.130|38.112.92.130]] ([[User talk:38.112.92.130|talk]]) 18:43, 17 October 2011 (UTC)</span><!-- Template:Unsigned IP --> <!--Autosigned by SineBot-->

