== "Original Version" not the original ==

The song you have listed as the "original" isn't the original as it starts with the lyrics "Zar je morala doc" which is a different song composed around the same time. Today the two songs are usually sung together as one, alternating verses from each. But the two have different melodies and lyrics. I believe the 2nd version you have listed may be the original, but I'll have to check my sources, anyway it's certainly older than the one listed now as original.  <span style="font-size: smaller;" class="autosigned">— Preceding [[Wikipedia:Signatures|unsigned]] comment added by [[Special:Contributions/75.187.155.2|75.187.155.2]] ([[User talk:75.187.155.2|talk]]) 00:10, 20 August 2013 (UTC)</span><!-- Template:Unsigned IP --> <!--Autosigned by SineBot-->
